:0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T00:57:25.000Z","msg":"Smartthings / hubitat"},{"pid":"97b6886e7f714ba52a2a59aa0119b82976038f53","tid":1423564,"uid":41458,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T00:57:50.000Z","msg":"Smarthome 係香港根本係多鳩餘<br />\n成本高，仲要maintain D hardware<br />\n又唔覺得特別方便<br />\n根本係卓頭"},{"pid":"6cd64f5d315360394d6d8e86fd5b1740fa2c2bbf","tid":1423564,"uid":60605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:03:52.000Z","msg":"留名，想問下係咪控唔到紅外線？因為屋企風扇同冷氣個remote 都係用紅外線"},{"pid":"64f719f3fef47d54eabfe078447136d2aa494c94","tid":1423564,"uid":81340,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:25:43.000Z","msg":"我自己一直有接觸開home automation<br />\n但裝之前要諗<br />\n1)  你係唔係有好多多餘錢, 香港都有唔少豪宅裝, 都係用外國野加搵埋公司做保養, 因為好多牌子都唔係open source, 你只可以搵返同一間做改動<br />\n2）你間屋可能要大裝修, 每間屋嘅電線廻路都唔同, 原本設計係冇位放個module, 你加上去只會唔好睇, 又或者你見自動窗簾好靚但你本身冇電位係窗簾旁<br />\n3）換電器未必控製到, 以電視為例, 有電視可以行232/IP(好少）, 多數行ir, 但唔同電視牌子, 唔同model 都唔一樣, 隨時換完電視又要比多幾千蚊改code<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有心玩就買個raspberry pi 自己試吓, 一定做到其他牌子嘅工能"},{"pid":"4f2a5d049960132189d313f9edad4c8c6fd7f621","tid":1423564,"uid":8880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:33:36.000Z","msg":"remote開電腦有冇人有經驗?<br />\n試過搞wake-on-lan 但搞極都極唔到"},{"pid":"87b1ae776dccc921fea1cb7d3097ac50e1afa22c","tid":1423564,"uid":298075,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4f2a5d049960132189d313f9edad4c8c6fd7f621","tid":1423564,"uid":8880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:33:36.000Z","msg":"remote開電腦有冇人有經驗?<br />\n試過搞wake-on-lan 但搞極都極唔到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T02:10:21.000Z","msg":"Router 有冇設好？<br />\n有分外網同內網嘅wol<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wsvXuED.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwsvXuED.png&h=800769ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你用開邊隻router?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d0c4ffe2b4002360f5c45f43bf7d5ca3814e